新墨西哥州和纽约州的总检察长。 “KOSA 将建立更好的保障措施......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299941/state-ag-letter-congress-pass-child -safety-kosa-deadline&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299941/state-ag-letter-congress-pass-child-safety-kosa-deadline" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299941/state-ag-letter-congress-pass-child-safety-kosa-deadline</id><author><name>阿迪·罗伯逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-18T17:52:21-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-18T17:52:21-05:00</updated><title>据报道，美国律师将试图迫使谷歌出售 Chrome 并分拆 Android</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木槌在 Google 徽标上投下阴影的照片插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/t-eGYb-862fvWQExuTQoLHWmThU=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873 /cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73731989/236780_Google_AntiTrust_Trial_Custom_Art_CVirginia__0000_4.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;bdxWmg&quot; >;司法部计划要求谷歌反垄断审判法官在法官裁定该公司后强制该公司出售其 Chrome 浏览器&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/5 /24155520/judge-rules-on-us-doj-v-google-antitrust-search-suit&quot;>;维持非法搜索垄断&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/ news/articles/2024-11-18/doj-will-push-google-to-sell-off-chrome-to-break-search-monopoly&quot;>;报道&lt;em>;彭博社&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em >;.&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;mLYBMh&quot;>;Chrome 是世界上使用最广泛的浏览器，政府律师辩称，将其用于交叉推广 Google 产品是限制可用渠道的因素之一以及促进竞争发展的激励措施。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;eQ0hHO&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem -component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;司法部希望如何打破谷歌的搜索垄断&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9 /24265983/doj-google-search-remedies-monopoly&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;美国诉谷歌：搜索反垄断对决的所有新闻&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com /23869483/us-v-google-search-antitrust-case-updates&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;zX8tRW&quot;>;官员准备提出的要求包括谷歌将 Android 从搜索和 Google Play 中分离出来，但并没有试图迫使谷歌出售 Android。另一项要求是必须与广告商分享更多信息，并“给予他们更多控制权......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18 /24300033/doj-google-monopoly-remedies-search-chrome-android-ai&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24300033/doj-google-monopoly-remedies-search-chrome-android-ai" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24300033/doj-google-monopoly-remedies-search-chrome-android-ai</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-18T17:46:05-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-18T17:46:05-05:00</updated><title>亚马逊和 SpaceX 在法庭上攻击美国劳工监管机构</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;US-UNION-RETAIL-AMAZON&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/enRQlETJfgrgqquHGdMQQV3Pr4I=/0x53:4469x3032/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73731977/1239668458.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：ANDREA RENAULT/AFP via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;E4qK5v&quot;>;亚马逊和 SpaceX 正在寻求限制国家劳动关系委员会，要求法院宣布其维护劳动法的程序违宪。但当两家公司周一提出论点时，三人小组的法官似乎持怀疑态度。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;TnpglV&quot;>;在第五巡回上诉法院审理的两起不同案件中，两家公司辩称 NLRB非法强迫他们参与涉嫌反劳工行为的行政诉讼。亚马逊案件的核心是&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reuters.com/legal/government/amazon-loses-challenge-unions-election-win-nyc-warehouse-2024-08-30/&quot;>;是否SpaceX 的案件涉及前员工的指控，他们声称自己在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com 后被解雇/2022/11/17/23464180/spacex-employees-fired-elon-musk-charges-national-labor-relations-board&quot;>;批评首席执行官埃隆·马斯克&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot; aRTHTq&quot;>;裁决...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299607/amazon-spacex-nlrb-labor-law-fifth-电路&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299607/amazon-spacex-nlrb-labor-law-fifth-circuit" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299607/amazon-spacex-nlrb-labor-law-fifth-Circuit</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-18T17:25:16-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-18T17:25:16-05:00</updated><title> Razzlekhan，加密货币领域最尴尬的说唱歌手，即将入狱</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;屏幕截图显示希瑟·摩根蹲在混凝土表面上，双手握拳放在身前。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0rRPPa03bgBjur5onUS-ul8DXzw=/149x0:2429x1520/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73731921/razzlekhan_rap_music_crypto.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;屏幕截图：Razzlekhan&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;gooktT&quot;>;联邦法官判处 Heather Morgan 18 个月监禁，罪名是帮助丈夫 Ilya “Dutch” Lichtenstein 洗钱被盗的比特币, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coindesk.com/policy/2024/11/18/bitfinex-hack-launderer-heather-razlekhan-morgan-sentenced-to-18-months-in-prison/&quot;>; &lt;em>;CoinDesk&lt;/em>; 报告&lt;/a>;。 Lichtenstein 承认在 2016 年入侵了加密货币交易所 Bitfinex，窃取了 120,000 枚比特币，价值&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/hacker-s-wife-razlekhan- gets-18-months-for-money-laundering&quot;>;当时为 7100 万美元&lt;/a>;（截至撰写本文时已接近 110 亿美元）。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;co9eXK&quot;>;在她被捕之前，摩根是&lt;em>;福布斯&lt;/em>;和&lt;em>;公司的成员。博主。当司法部宣布逮捕她时，互联网发现她&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/15/24297157/bitfinex-hacker-sentenced-crypto-bitcoin-heist&quot;>;还以“Razzlekhan”的名义制作了以加密货币为主题的说唱视频&lt;/a>;。整个故事预计将在 Netflix 的纪录片系列和名为《Dutch &amp;amp; Dutch》的电影中永垂不朽。 Razzlekhan。&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;ljX6Zj&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem- component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;我从涉嫌比特币洗钱者 Razzlekhan 的言语和韵律中学到了什么&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22924237/razlekhan -bitfinex-hack-laundering-bitcoin-explained-rapper-heather-morgan&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;5LxdDZ&quot;>;摩根 &lt;a href=&quot;https: //x.com/HeatherReyhan/status/1858620639898186086&quot;>;针对 X 发表声明&lt;/a>;，称她“很快就会告诉我的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299934/razlekhan-crypto-bitfinex-hack-heather-morgan&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299934/razzlekhan-crypto-bitfinex-hack-heather-morgan" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299934/razlekhan-crypto-bitfinex-hack-heather-morgan</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-18T16:45:17-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-18T16:45:17-05:00</updated><title> Corsair 现已推出适用于 Mac 的游戏键盘和鼠标</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;桌子上的冰川蓝色 Corsair K65 Plus 无线键盘和 M75 无线鼠标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8VlKlDqGGOH0nGLwFTfwhRC9Qqk=/0x0:2500x1667/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73731830/corsair1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Corsair 升级了其 K65 Plus 无线键盘和 M75 无线鼠标，因此它们与 Mac 兼容，并具有新的配色。&lt;/em>; |图片：Corsair&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OiQjtB&quot;>;Corsair 有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.corsair.com/c/482924/490888/8513?u=https%3A% 2F%2Fwww.corsair.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-release%2Fcorsair-unveils-exclusive-award-making-k65-plus-wireless-keyboard-and-m75-wireless-gaming-mouse-colorways-for-mac%3Futm_source% 3D95368%26utm_medium%3DAffiliate%26utm_campaign%3D1498468_Main%2520Page%26utm_content%3DCorsair%26clickid%3DVQF2hWUIXxyKWEx3n%253AQzIWnLUkCQ3JSfPy2CWc0%26utm_coupon%3D%26ir gwc%3D1&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;宣布K65 Plus 无线键盘的更新版本&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.corsair.com/c/482924/490888/8513?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corsair.com %2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-release%2Fcorsair-launches-new-75-keyboard-for-enthusiast-gamers&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;今年早些时候首次亮相&lt;/a>;现在与 Mac 兼容。 Corsair M75 无线鼠标的新版本也加入其中，这两款外围设备均提供 Mac 独有的颜色，包括冰川蓝和该公司称为霜冻的白色版本。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;hfdX3O&quot;>;霜冻版本&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/shop/product/HRYZ2ZM/A/corsair-k65-plus-wireless-mechanical-gaming-keyboard-for-mac&quot;>;K65 Plus 无线键盘&lt;/a >; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/shop/product/HRYT2ZM/A/corsair-m75-wireless-lightweight-rgb-gaming-mouse&quot;>;M75 无线鼠标&lt;/a>; 现已上市Apple 在线商店和零售店售价分别为 179.95 美元和 129.95 美元。冰川蓝色版本将以相同的价格提供，但会在晚些时候推出。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Corsair&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Mac Corsair K65 Plus 无线键盘版本仅提供冰川蓝和霜白色（白色）...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/11/18/24299881/corsair-mac-k65-plus-wireless-gaming-keyboard-m75-mouse&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299881/corsair-mac-k65-plus-wireless-gaming-keyboard-m75-mouse" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299881/corsair-mac-k65-plus-wireless-gaming-keyboard-m75-mouse</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-18T16:25:28-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-18T16:25:28-05:00</updated><title>哈珀柯林斯 (HarperCollins) 要求作者授权他们的书籍用于人工智能培训</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一张有故障的铅笔在纸上书写的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ByW_TIkAhckXB_iJJSVYlIULBUE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73731765/STK149_AI_Writing.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Hugo Herrera / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;MSXnGs&quot;>;HarperCollins 已与一家未透露姓名的人工智能技术公司达成协议，允许该公司使用一些非小说类书籍来训练其模型，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.404media.co/harpercollins-ai-deal/&quot;>;&lt;em>;404 Media &lt;/em>; 报道&lt;/a>;，但前提是作者选择将其书籍用于训练。一些作者目前正在起诉 OpenAI 等公司，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/20/23882140/george-rr-martin-lawsuit-openai-copyright-infringement&quot;>;指控&lt;/ a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/20/24224450/anthropic-copyright-lawsuit-pilated-books-ai&quot;>;他们&lt;/a>;因训练人工智能模型而侵犯版权&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rkBSyt&quot;>;根据 HarperCollins 向 &lt;em>;404 Media 提供的声明，该协议保护作者的“其作品的潜在价值以及我们的共享收入”和版税流。”作者 Daniel Kibblesmith &lt;a href=&quot;https://bsky.app/profile/kibblesmith.com/post/3laz4ryav3k2w?ref=404media.co&quot;>;发布了一封电子邮件的屏幕截图&lt;/a>;，显示如果满足以下条件，他将获得 2,500 美元的报酬：他允许他的一本书获得许可。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;eJ42DW&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;bluesky-embed&quot; data-bluesky-uri=&quot;at://did:plc:dmht6n3frexsulkabk4vtrdm/app. bsky.feed.post/3laz4ryav3k2w&quot; data-bluesky-cid=&quot;bafyreifabpnrwp6fnc2tutcgbrf3ffcslo5pd3xc2vlqwx3fbgeqc2cejm&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot;>;可恶。&lt;/p>;— &lt;a href=&quot;https://bsky.app/profile/did: plc:dmht6n3frexsulkabk4vtrdm?ref_src=embed&quot;>;丹尼尔·基布尔史密斯 (@kibblesmith.com)&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:dmht6n3frexsulkabk4vtrdm/post/3laz4ryav3k2w?ref_src=embed&quot; >;2...&lt;/a>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299882/harpercollins-authors-license-books -ai-training&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299882/harpercollins-authors-license-books-ai-training" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/18/24299882/harpercollins-authors-license-books-ai-training</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry></feed>